edu.nyu.cs.javagit.api

Class GitVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.nyu.cs.javagit.api.GitVersion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandResponse, java.lang.Comparable<GitVersion>

    public class GitVersion
extends java.lang.Object
implements CommandResponse, java.lang.Comparable<GitVersion>
    Git version is composed by major.minor.releaseMajor{"." + releaseMinor|"-" + tag} meaning that release minor and tag are optional and mutually excluded.
    These rules are valid for Git v1.1.0 onwards. This object is not intended to manage Git versions previous to this one

    Valid values are : 1.7.0, 1.8.0.1 and 1.8.2-rc4 among others
